parameters.name: CredentialConfig
parameters.description:
**If you have no special requirements, leave this parameter empty.**

The authorization chain settings. For more information, see [Use authorization chains to access resources of other entities](~~465340~~).

parameters.name: ProjectName
parameters.description: The name of the project. For more information, see [CreateProject](~~478153~~).

parameters.name: SourceURI
parameters.description:
The Object Storage Service (OSS) URI of the file.

Specify the URI in the oss://${Bucket}/${Object} format. ${Bucket} specifies the name of an OSS bucket that is in the same region as the current project. ${Object} specifies the path of the object with the extension included.
